Class RepositoryManager.RepositoryManagerMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.enterprise.admin.servermgmt.RepositoryManager.RepositoryManagerMessages
  • Enclosing class:
    RepositoryManager

    protected static class RepositoryManager.RepositoryManagerMessages
extends Object
    The RepositoryManagerMessages class is used to abstract out ResourceBundle messages that are specific to a domain, node-agent, or server instance.
